Pro'; font-size:12pt">the</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:1.4pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">best</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:0.6pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">of</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; letter-spacing:0.6pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">times.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:122%; margin:0pt 10.4pt 0pt 22.1pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-16.55pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">3.2 66 </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">additional</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">back office staff were deployed into the Terminal buildings to assist passengers.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:122%; margin:0pt 10.4pt 0pt 22.1pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-16.55pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">3.3 Overall on 24 December of the originally scheduled 258 departures, 186 departed the airport, albeit some with delays.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:122%; margin:0pt 10.4pt 0pt 22.1pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-16.55pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">3.4 However 67 of the North Terminal depa</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">rtures were ultimately cancelled, many of them quite late in the day.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:122%; margin:0pt 10.4pt 0pt 22.1pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-16.55pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">3.5 A rapid recovery enabled Gatwick to fly a full schedule on Christmas Day, Boxing Day and onwards.</span></p><p style="line-height:14pt; margin:0.85pt 0pt 0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 5.15pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">4.</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; letter-spacing:2.2pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Flood </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Preparations</span></p><p style="line-height:13pt; margin:0.75pt 0pt 0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:122%; margin:0pt 10.4pt 0pt 22.1pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-16.55pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">4.1 Since the change of ownership</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">in 2009, Gatwick has, </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">with the full backing of its new shareholders, invested over £1bn with the end aim of transforming Gatwick into a world-leading airport</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">capable of competing successfully.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:122%; margin:0pt 10.4pt 0pt 22.1pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-16.55pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">4.2 This investment programme included over £20 million in mitigating and alleviating</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> flood risk.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:122%; margin:0pt 10.4pt 0pt 22.1pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-16.55pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">4.3 The majority of this investment</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">has been focused on the South Terminal, which had been assessed as having a 1 in 20 year risk of flooding. These works were successful in preventing flooding of the</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">South Terminal during the recent exception</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">al weather.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:122%; margin:0pt 10.4pt 0pt 22.1pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-16.55pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">4.4 The North Terminal had been assessed in 2008 as being at a low risk of flooding- less than a 1in 100 year risk.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:122%; margin:0pt 10.4pt 0pt 22.1pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-16.55pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">4.5 Gatwick will be working with the Environment</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">Agency to reassess all flood modeling, and provides</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">an unqualified assurance th</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">at all necessary further</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">investment will be carried out as a matter</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">of urgency.</span></p><p style="line-height:12pt; margin:0.65pt 0pt 0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 11.9pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">5.</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; letter-spacing:2.2pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Passengers</span></p><p style="line-height:14pt; margin:0.85pt 0pt 0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:122%; margin:0pt 10.4pt 0pt 22.1pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-16.55pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">5.1 Despite the lack of warning and despite the flooding</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">and the subsequent loss of the switch rooms at the North Terminal it is clear that there is a lot more</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> Gatwick could ·and should · have done with</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">its airport partners to help make the disruption as painless as possible for passengers.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:122%; margin:0pt 10.4pt 0pt 22.1pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-16.55pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">5.2 Gatwick did attempt to communicate</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">with passengers via twitter, issuing over 300 tweets</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">on the day. It also issued thre</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">e media statements</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">which were sent to key news rooms and media outlets</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">as well as briefing local and national media throughout the day.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:122%; margin:0pt 10.4pt 0pt 22.1pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-16.55pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">5.3 As an Airport</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">Gatwick sets itself very high standards in performance and customer service. It </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">has worked hard along </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">with its airport</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">partners to achieve a good reputation for dealing with disruptions. On this occasion Gatwick's actions and those of its airport</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">partners fell short.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:122%; margin:0pt 10.4pt 0pt 22.1pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-16.55pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">5.4 Gatwick has offered</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">each passenger whose flight was cancelled £100 of high street vouc</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">hers as a goodwill gesture. The McMillan review {see 6.1) will focus in particular</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">on how Gatwick can learn the lessons for the future. At times like this passenger information and comfort must always be a priority.</span></p><p style="line-height:12pt; margin:0.65pt 0pt 0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 11.5pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">6.</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; letter-spacing:2.2pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Review</span></p><p style="line-height:14pt; margin:0.85pt 0pt 0pt 14.2pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:122%; margin:0pt 10.4pt 0pt 22.1pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-16.55pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">6.1 David McMillan, a Non </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">Executive Director at Gatwick, is leading a comprehensive review of what happened, the lessons that can be learnt and what actions are required to avoid a reoccurrence.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:122%; margin:0pt 10.4pt 0pt 22.1pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-16.55pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">6.2 David McMillan is Chair of the Board of Governors of the Flight Safety Foundation a</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">nd was Director</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">General of Eurocontrol, which co-ordinates air traffic</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">across 40 European states, from 2008 to 2012. Before that he was UK Director General of Civil Aviation and spoke for Europe on environmental issues at ICAO. Earlier in his career, he </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">led for Government on the establishment</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">of the NATS PPP and was Secretary to the RUCATSE study on airport</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">capacity in South East England. David started his career in the Diplomatic Service and is a fellow</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">of both the Chartered Institute of</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">Transport and th</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">e Royal Aeronautical Society.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:122%; margin:0pt 10.4pt 0pt 22.1pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-16.55pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">6.3 The Review will be published in February.</span></p><p style="line-height:14pt; margin:0.85pt 0pt 0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 11.15pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">7.</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; letter-spacing:1.85pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Conclusion</span></p><p style="line-height:14pt; margin:0.85pt 0pt 0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:122%; margin:0pt 10.4pt 0pt 22.1pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-16.55pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">7.1 There is never a good time for something like this to happen but Gatwick Airport recognises that Christmas Eve is probably the worst with so many passengers tr</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">avelling to be with their families over the festive period.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:122%; margin:0pt 10.4pt 0pt 22.1pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-16.55pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">7.2 Gatwick Airport</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">will learn the lessons, make any additional</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">investment required</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">and continue</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">to do everything it can to give its customers the quality of service they should expect.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:122%; margin:0pt 10.4pt 0pt 22.1pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-16.55pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">7.3 Gatwic</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">k Airport's Chief Executive extends a sincere apology to those whose travel plans were disrupted.</span></p><p style="line-height:8.5pt; margin:0.25pt 0pt 0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 5.05pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">January</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; letter-spacing:1.4pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">2014</span></p><p style="line-height:7.5pt; margin:0.5pt 0pt 0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="line-height:10pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="line-height:10pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="line-height:10pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="line-height:10pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="line-height:10pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="line-height:10pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="line-height:10pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="line-height:10pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="line-height:10pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="line-height:10pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="line-height:10pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 230.5pt 0pt 239pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">2</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div></body></html>